Interface MyMultiset<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the elements of the multiset.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CoarseGrainedMultiset, FineGrainedMultiset, LazyMultiset, LazyMultiset2, LockFreeMultiset

    public interface MyMultiset<T>
    The interface for a multiset (a set in which allows repetitions of the same element).
    Author:
    Orlando Leombruni
    See Also:
    CoarseGrainedMultiset, FineGrainedMultiset, LazyMultiset, LockFreeMultiset
